{"title":"和平之鸟","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平之鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为第一颗人造卫星而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高空里有一只神鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云彩上快乐欢叫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要和众星竞赛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地发出信号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它环绕地球运行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻正飞到北京；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十分钟以后它还要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含着微笑路过华盛顿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼你和平之鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃人造的星！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以人类的天才，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭开宇宙的秘密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于你我们将驾着火箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在星际中间旅行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和火星去握手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和月亮去谈心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要对月亮说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的那一棵银树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么隐藏几万年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不肯让我们去探索？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也快要出世了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把果子投向人间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投向莫斯科红场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者是投向天安门！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——10月7日夜11时左右，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻讯号声作"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}